{"tid":2258486,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國企爆煲華晨汽車債務違約10億，華晨回應「集團正積極研究解決」","createTime":"2020-10-26T05:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T01:09:29.000Z","uid":38539,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"96fc430db8aa873c335e0e8b6bd1181f5ea168a9","tid":2258486,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bd3ibFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbd3ibFp.jpg&h=6aa33c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華晨中國 （1114）母公司華晨汽車集團近日被爆債務違約，其私募債券「17華汽05」未能按期10月23日兌付，債券餘額為10億元（人民幣）。華晨集團為寶馬（BMW）在中國的主要合作夥伴，近月屢傳陷債務危機，但這次是首次發生實質性違約，華晨已回應指「集團正在積極研究解決」，並正在與投資者協商兌付事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201025/J7FKZD5JFZAXLH2M4C7YNIK5EE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201025%2FJ7FKZD5JFZAXLH2M4C7YNIK5EE%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oHG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=d0a76fdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201025%2FJ7FKZD5JFZAXLH2M4C7YNIK5EE%2F&h=735c1ae3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201025/J7FKZD5JFZAXLH2M4C7YNIK5EE/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個月前，華晨汽車就傳出負債千億瀕臨破產，員工要被迫放假的新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2156644/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2156644/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c834a19046d132283b9bc7354ef58682a63f7dea","tid":2258486,"uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbtFp1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbtFp1a.png&h=4f9aff1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbbe04802358dbcd86082f2fef64b257ca6b9539","tid":2258486,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"學含大咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj