faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"呢10億只係華晨汽車2017年推出的債券，今年到期要找數俾人，<br />\n但依家咁大間公司連10億都拎唔到出嚟，表示間公司資金真係出現問題。"},{"pid":"a57d008803098dd4e7e9d7985c96ddb0c07874da","tid":2258486,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"債轉股就可以解決"},{"pid":"18de687f7b45b1006560aabd6bdd76e5c535b012","tid":2258486,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"新浪新聞資料比較詳盡，雖然係殘體<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/2020-10-26/doc-iiznezxr8063585.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fchanjing%2Fgsnews%2F2020-10-26%2Fdoc-iiznezxr8063585.shtml&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oHG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=9b2ae3c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/2020-10-26/doc-iiznezxr8063585.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n公開數據顯示，截至今年一季度末，華晨集團負債總額為1226.75億元，佔資產總額的69.93%。其中有息債務674.72億元，佔總負債的比例超過一半；短期債務金額為483.96億元，長期債務金額為190.75億元。<br />\n<br />\n  不僅如此，華晨集團共存續15只債券，存量規模為175.73億元。其中2020年年內到期的債券金額為13.73億元，2021年到期的債券金額為65億元。共有101億元將於1~3年內到期，61億元將於3~5年內到期。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;這些債券的配額和期限是錯綜複雜的，就像連環套一樣。華晨集團前期借了不少債，一旦有一筆沒有按時兌付，就會影響後續的債券兌付。&rdquo;全聯車商投資管理（北京）有限公司總裁曹鶴說。"},{"pid":"016821983127e4f52b32d0470352b433130cd707","tid":2258486,"uid":9230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"債轉股，債主變債仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa105ffea10b44b8e9e6932cd89df74b8882c831","tid":2258486,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:53:57.000Z","msg":"解決提出還債嘅人就可以了，驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8542a1442c0fa117870fe1152f8e35